@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_kndbyy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(0.62)
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.exp(v1))
    v1 = ((0.62 / (tmp + 0.58 - v2 + 0.78)) + wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.81)))
    tmp = 0.39
    tmp = ((v1 * wp.abs(tmp + 0.90)) - ((v0 + 0.13 * v1 + 0.40) / (v1 + 0.07 / v0 + 0.01)))
    data[tid] = v0
